course_title: Principles and Practices of Injury Prevention

sections.comments: Classroom location: SPPH B112Please note, because of DL course-conflict scheduling issues, please double check to make sure this course does not conflict with any of the other courses you have registered in this term.

description: Injury epidemiology; surveillance; development, implementation, and evaluation techniques of preventive strategies; determinants of health; social marketing; injury policy; evidence-based prevention strategies; utilization of injury datasets.
